org.apache.ambari.server.stack

Interface StackDefinitionModule<T,I>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseModule, ComponentModule, ConfigurationModule, ExtensionModule, QuickLinksConfigurationModule, ServiceModule, StackModule, ThemeModule

    public interface StackDefinitionModule<T,I>
    Stack Definition Module. Represents a module within a stack definition tree. For each stack version specified in a stack definition a tree will exist with a stack module being the root node. Each module may have a parent as well as child modules. Each module has an associated "info" object which contains the underlying state that is being wrapped by the module.
